s fire’s embrace.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">The Marana Forni oven roars to life, transforming each bite into charred perfection. Far from ordinary, live seafood tanks meet a dry-aging lamb cabinet. It’s a myth waiting to unfold. A testament to provenance and passion.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">Welcome to <em>Dark Shepherd</em>.<br>Born of fire. Bound by flavour.</p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 0px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n\n\n  }\n\n  #block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 3% 3% 3% 3%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  .fe-block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n.fe-block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  .fe-block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 {\n      --tweak-text-block-blend\n  : normal;\n    }\n  \n\n  .fe-block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 {\n    --blur-value: blur(0px);}\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-395c53c3c348741c7cd5 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n      \n    </style>\n\n  \n\n\n</div>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"fe-block fe-block-337fe9eecaab4be3a7b4\"><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.c