v class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-html html-block\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/82801178-b7bb-43c4-a910-6b0ca726dd8c_518/website.components.html.styles.css&quot;]\" data-block-scripts=\"[&quot;https://definitions.sqspcdn.com/website-component-definition/static-assets/website.components.html/82801178-b7bb-43c4-a910-6b0ca726dd8c_518/website.components.html.visitor.js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"fc13b32a8156a9158fcc\" id=\"block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Craft an event that awakens a world of sensation. This is no mere gathering; it’s a rite of passage. An invitation to something beyond the ordinary.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Elect the 120-seat dining room for your revel, embellished with sandy beige booths and marble tables. Or, retreat into the private 10-seater, for those seeking a shadow of secrecy. Each corner of the space beckons with an intoxicating sense of possibility.</p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n\n\n  }\n\n  #block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  .fe-block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n.fe-block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  .fe-block-fc13b32a8156a9158fcc {\n      --tweak