"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">Branding and design by <a href=\"https://www.allocreative.com.au\">Allo Creative</a></p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-36ee380f333ec318e23a {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-36ee380f333ec318e23a .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  .fe-block-36ee380f333ec318e23a {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n.fe-block-36ee380f333ec318e23a {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  .fe-block-36ee380f333ec318e23a {\n      --tweak-text-block-blend\n  : normal;\n    }\n  \n\n  .fe-block-36ee380f333ec318e23a {\n    --blur-value: blur(15px);}\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-36ee380f333ec318e23a {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-36ee380f333ec318e23a .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n      \n    </style>\n\n  \n\n\n</div>\n</div></div></div></div></div>\n    </div>\n  \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n</footer>\n\n      \n    </div>\n\n    <script defer=\"true\" src=\"https://static1.squarespace.com/static/vta/5c5a519771c10ba3470d8101/scripts/site-bundle.24618f321442829cf50ddb341e64781c.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" version=\"1.1\" style=\"display:none\" data-usage=\"social-icons-svg\"><symbol id=\"instagram-unauth-icon\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\"><pa