id: 63
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I’ll use a charcoal dining-room base, white identity marks, restrained brass accent, editorial serif display, and photography-led panels. The page rhythm will be: home concept → menu pathway → functions → contact, with the existing reservation, menu, gift voucher, social, phone, and The Star Brisbane location intent preserved."}

