data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_12","content":"16:<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable di\"/>\n22:<meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable di\"/>\n30:<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable di\"/>\n31:<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Discover Dark Shepherd at The Star Brisbane, a lamb-focused Mediterranean restaurant blending bold flavours with sophisticated flair. Featuring White Pyrenees lamb, a state-of-the-art woodfire oven, and a moody, stylish atmosphere, it’s the perfect destination for elegant lunches or unforgettable dinners. Reserve your table today.\" />\n41:<script data-name=\"static-context\">Static = window.Static || {}; Static.SQUARESPACE_CONTEXT = {\"betaFeatureFlags\":[\"campaigns_merch_state\",\"nested_categories\",\"modernized-pdp-m2-enabled\",\"enable_modernized_pdp_m3_fluid\",\"campaigns_thumbnail_layout\",\"campaigns_import_discounts\",\"member_areas_feature\",\"i18n_beta_website_locales\",\"campaigns_new_image_layout_picker\",\"supports_versioned_template_assets\",\"enable_form_submission_trigger\",\"contacts_and_campaigns_redesign\",\"c