kit.com/cards?accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&venueid=12275&theme=dark&accent=157,157,157%C2%A0\"  target=\"_blank\" >Dark Shepherd Gift Voucher</a>\n1129:              <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&venueid=14196&theme=light&accent=157,157,157\"  target=\"_blank\" >Tassis Group Gift Voucher</a>\n1240:                    href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\"\n1267:    <span hidden class=\"js-header-burger-open-title visually-hidden\">Open Menu</span>\n1268:    <span hidden class=\"js-header-burger-close-title visually-hidden\">Close Menu</span>\n1287:    <!-- (Mobile) Menu Navigation -->\n1299:&quot;href&quot;: &quot;https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant&quot;,\n1491:              <!-- Menu Navigation -->\n1505:                <span class=\"header-nav-folder-title-text\">Menus</span>\n1524:                        Main Menu\n1552:                        The Daylight Banquet | 57pp\n1566:                        Banquets\n1622:                  Functions\n1640:                <span class=\"header-nav-folder-title-text\">Gift Vouchers</span>\n1655:                    <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards?accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&venueid=12275&theme=dark&accent=157,157,157%C2%A0\"  target=\"_blank\" >Dark Shepherd Gift Voucher</a>\n1662:                    <a href=\"https://giftcards.nowbookit.com/cards/card-selection?accountid=4843949d-9776-494d-8655-478ef32b5105&venueid=14196&theme=light&accent=157,157,157\"  target=\"_blank\" >Tassis Group Gift Voucher</a>\n1776:                href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\"\n2494:      href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\" \n2515:      href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\" \n3092:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h2 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\">The flock gathers.</h2><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">By night, the embers smoulder, lamb surrenders, and flavours rise like whispered secrets.<br>By day, the sun lends its warmth, casting light on Mediterranean marvels. Here, the dark and the bright find harmony. Lamb, revered as the heart of the feast, meets fire’s embrace.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">The Marana Forni oven roars to life, transforming each bite into charred perfection. Far from ordinary, live seafood tanks meet a dry-aging lamb cabinet. It’s a myth waiting to unfold. A testament to provenance and passion.</p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">Welcome to <em>Dark Shepherd</em>.<br>Born of fire. Bound by flavour.</p></div>\n3176:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><h1 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Mediterranean RESTAURANT AT THE STAR BRISBANE</h1></span></div></div>\n3276:      Menu\n3297:      Menu\n3356:      Banquets\n3377:      Banquets\n3480:  <svg class=\"section-divider-svg-stroke\" viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n4591:  <svg class=\"section-divider-svg-stroke\" viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n4953:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">A bold awakening of Mediterranean flavours, succulent cuts, and a menu tailored for those who crave an unmatched intensity. White Pyrenees lamb, the wagyu of its kind, leads the flock, followed by an artistry of seafood and tender grilled meats, all baptised by fire. A timeless tradition, delivered with provenance and passion. Uncover the offerings.</p></div>\n5199:  data-src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb\"\n5200:  data-image=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb\"\n5206:  data-load=\"false\" elementtiming=\"system-image-block\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb\" width=\"1365\" height=\"2048\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" style=\"display:block;object-position: var(--image-component-focal-point);object-fit: var(--image-component-object-fit);\" srcset=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=100w 100w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=300w 300w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=500w 500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=750w 750w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=1000w 1000w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=1500w 1500w, https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/659f48a97a40b977345eec2d/8d1d65d8-106c-476c-883e-01f856a4f281/Slow+cooked+lamb?format=2500w 2500w\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-loader=\"sqs\">\n5417:  <svg class=\"section-divider-svg-stroke\" viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n6243:  <svg class=\"section-divider-svg-stroke\" viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n7069:  <svg class=\"section-divider-svg-stroke\" viewBox=\"0 0 1 1\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n8010:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>WHEN THE EMBERS GLOW</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>All Day Dining </strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>7 Days • 11am-Late<br></strong>Open every day except Christmas Day</p></div>\n8094:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>FIND US</strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><strong>The Terrace, Level 4</strong> <br>The Star Brisbane<br><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--white\">Ph. </span><a href=\"tel:+61721116869\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"sqsrte-text-color--white\">(07) 2111 6869</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\"><a href=\"/careers\"><strong>Careers</strong></a><strong><br></strong><a href=\"https://www.tassisgroup.com.au/business-opportunities\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Business Opportunities</strong></a></p></div>\n8178:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\" class=\"\">🅿 Free validated parking for diners.</p></div>\n","isError":false}

